data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the highly sought-after North Forsyth location. Boasting a finished basement, this residence offers versatile space for additional bedrooms or flex use, complementing the master suite conveniently situated on the main level. The property rests on a stunning over half-acre lot within an established and meticulously maintained neighborhood—what’s more, no HOA fees. Inside, tall ceilings accentuate the open floor plan, creating an inviting ambiance throughout. The living room features a captivating stone fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings. Situated within the amazing new East Forsyth High School district, this home is just a stone’s throw away from Lake Lanier, shopping centers, parks, and top-notch schools. Don’t miss this opportunity to embrace comfort, convenience, and a fantastic location in this wonderful abode.
